    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要剧情：</strong><br>扮演一名警察，负责调查2003年著名“Santа Margarita”学校发生的地震。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/b923dec21203ec54f5e94441472db1ae.poster.avif?t=1769298079\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/b923dec21203ec54f5e94441472db1ae.webm?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/b923dec21203ec54f5e94441472db1ae.mp4?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你的任务是揭开真相，探索学校的黑暗过去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/cc488da7d8c6ecd1538cfebb65af9a0c.poster.avif?t=1769298079\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/cc488da7d8c6ecd1538cfebb65af9a0c.webm?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/cc488da7d8c6ecd1538cfebb65af9a0c.mp4?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在调查过程中，你将经历各种无法解释的超自然现象……或者，你能解释吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/8af3a5c8e515519b779dbbd9fec91821.poster.avif?t=1769298079\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/8af3a5c8e515519b779dbbd9fec91821.webm?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/8af3a5c8e515519b779dbbd9fec91821.mp4?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，你需要在学校一楼完成一系列适度难度的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/37ebb4160c22d1a33b99deeca926b828.poster.avif?t=1769298079\" width=610 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/37ebb4160c22d1a33b99deeca926b828.webm?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228230/extras/37ebb4160c22d1a33b99deeca926b828.mp4?t=1769298079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时长约1.5小时</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >场景探索</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实风格画面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS复古风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >万圣节背景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >含血腥内容，不适合所有玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中等难度谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏将通过更新带来更多内容</p></li></ul>",
